{"tid":1305911,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[頂撚住]〈同路行〉原：周柏豪－我的宣言","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T04:05:29.000Z","uid":122380,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"341e95c62e87850f119a6025803cebeaa9142e9a","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=42z0OXfDciQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D42z0OXfDciQ&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=ea0c10a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=42z0OXfDciQ</a><br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n前路再難行，我地都要撐住。<br />\n多謝每一位願意挺身而出既香港人。<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n原曲：周柏豪〈我的宣言〉<br />\n原詞：陳詠謙<br />\n編曲：RANDY CHOW＆黃兆銘<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n〈同路行〉<br />\n主唱：野貓軍團<br />\n改詞：碧落<br />\n混音：怕醜仔<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n在這風雨日子 同渡<br />\n誰亦奮力拼出 地圖<br />\n就算槍棍亂掃 黑警千軍佈<br />\n阻不了你共我分毫<br />\n<br />\n或有一線曙光 浮露<br />\n浮露卻未照出 命途<br />\n前路未能定稿 花開翩翩起舞 <br />\n堅守不變信念 就算謊話再好 亦像佞言亂吐<br />\n<br />\n這一秒若沉默如被銷聲<br />\n這一仗若難耐仍願肩並<br />\n面對極權下烽煙 遍地哭聲 <br />\n硝煙散卻未撤走未停 唯求花開盼爭勝<br />\n <br />\n前路縱然密鋪 雲霧<br />\n雲霧散盡透出 命途<br />\n在這飄雨日子 花開翩翩起舞<br />\n堅守不變信念 如你我這願祟高<br />\n<br />\n這一秒若沉默如被銷聲<br />\n這一仗若難耐仍願肩並<br />\n未畏懼殘暴烽煙 遍地皆兵 <br />\n硝煙四散未撤走未停 <br />\n這一秒若沉默難逆轉勝<br />\n這一仗若難耐仍願一拼<br />\n亂世中若難過 你我同過 <br />\n傾出過 齊守衛去發聲  <br />\n<br />\n即使黑夜漫長無夢 你我志願永未化空 齊同遊同一青空  <br />\n<br />\n這一秒若沉默如被銷聲<br />\n這一仗若難耐仍願肩並<br />\n共對極權及黑警 遍地皆兵 <br />\n似水有散聚柔剛兼併 <br />\n這一秒若沉默難逆轉勝<br />\n這一仗若難耐仍願一拼<br />\n亂世中若難過 你我仍可 <br />\n傾出過 繁花遍開得勝"},{"pid":"e78eeb9e71d99d533355e2cba02dff5c2c3bb108","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"聽完記得去埋隔離post聽夕巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1304080/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1304080/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"d7413be91671fc33092a8172a28794e3dfc354d0","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxQDPtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxQDPtJ.jpg&h=013600f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8f8cf74464715475df037a44f11ee32cc52441a","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ec429f06c6c37e289a2994f926aac21540139f","tid":1305911,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"碧爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6c793f3e8c41ee5e026021b15e7fdd7d55de49","tid":1305911,"uid":87149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963f5c1ee3dbbbebda658a58a778285db6a6e20b","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ec429f06c6c37e289a2994f926aac21540139f","tid":1305911,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"碧爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"頂撚住"},{"pid":"5fdab67005eccc1fa149a420c4de36221c253fcd","tid":1305911,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6c793f3e8c41ee5e026021b15e7fdd7d55de49","tid":1305911,"uid":87149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0